items.bio: Hello my name is Gede Suyasa, a local of the island of Bali. I was born and raised on this beautiful island, and I hope that you come to enjoy it as well.
I am from Malaysia and I travel occasionally. Let's drink.
Still competitively Foursquares. I go to a lot of bars and vegan restaurants.
A free-spirited-pet-lovin-adrenaline-junkie journalist, globetrotter & self taught chef who turns into a tree huggin Hippie when in housewife mode.
James shows great appreciation for what he does at work and loves to creative ideas and opportunity to try new things.
I see,  i shoot,  i create memories ♥
